Two police officers are calling the homicide department. The attendant answers:
- Homicide Investigation Department, duty station l-nt Ivanov. Hello, I'm listening to you.
Teaching staff:
- Hello. This is the patrol service, Sergeant Petrov and Sergeant Sidorov.
Duty officer:
- What happened:
PPS-s:
- Murder. A thirty-five-year-old man was killed. His mother stabbed him nine times in the abdomen for walking on the freshly washed floor.
The attendant:
